nctioning of the state bureaucracy and also serves as a memoir of Landers' years in the state government.</p></scopecontent><c02 id="aspace_408cdf973e8765914b123f415c115ce4" level="file"><did><unittitle>"Michigan Seeks Better Management,"</unittitle><unitdate normal="1948/1948" type="inclusive">1948</unitdate><container label="Box" type="box">3</container></did></c02><c02 id="aspace_20398bf6161f03e1f3600048e0edcc5b" level="file"><did><unittitle>"State Administrative Reform in Michigan,"</unittitle><unitdate normal="1954/1954" type="inclusive">1954</unitdate><container label="Box" type="box">3</container></did></c02><c02 id="aspace_f9586b53b5000971a18e166d5aa9c2bd" level="file"><did><unittitle>Articles on Government</unittitle><unitdate certainty="approximate" normal="1974/1974" type="inclusive">circa 1974</unitdate><container label="Box" type="box">3</container></did></c02><c02 id="aspace_5c2f50f09097a5b472a6138749fd721d" level="file"><did><unittitle>"Local Government in Branch County,"</unittitle><unitdate normal="1975/1975" type="inclusive">1975</unitdate><container label="Box" type="box">3</container></did></c02><c02 id="aspace_c89ca6bb7ebb7f300015d1e97c03f232" level="file"><did><unittitle>"Michigan's Lawmakers,"</unittitle><unitdate normal="1983/1984" type="inclusive">1983-1984</unitdate><container label="Box" type="box">3</container></did></c02><c02 id="aspace_54d4244b89842eb754bc727d483a2e73" level="file"><did><unittitle><title render="italic">A Bureaucratic View of Michigan State Government, 1935-1960</title></unittitle><unitdate normal="1988/1988" type="inclusive">1988</unitdate><container label="Box" type="box">3</container></did></c02><c02 id="aspace_6224021a89fe6c1928f6a6c9c591526a" level="file"><did><unittitle>Correspondence re <title render="italic">A Bureaucratic View</title></unittitle><unitdate normal="1987/1989" type="inclusive">1987-1989</unitdate><container label="Box" type="box">3</container></did></c02><c02 id="aspace_3b9d60a781a7e8feee27619c7b9